& [SOPAttentionMemoryCodecRealization062] is the realized attention-memory frame
  + [moment] is the photonic stream becomes memory when route colors, source pointers, relation edges, and reconstruction seeds can be written and read again
  + [focus] is SOP attention memory codec
  + [periphery] is visual anchors, image parsing, color-routed meaning, semantic hashes, relation graphs, study subjects, and concept-development traces
  + [boundary] is visible symbolic reentry through SOP records; not hidden activations, exact KV cache, or perfect replay
  + [outside] is unprovided images, uninspected pixels, inaccessible hidden state, unstored source detail, and unsupported claims of exact recall
  + [impulse] is build a deep compression engine of attention from inspectable thinking nodes
  + [balance] is stable because memory is framed as auditable reconstruction with fidelity gates
  + [next_step] is use the codec as the memory surface for later study stores, concept traces, and model-lens reentry packets

  = must: preserve recall_fidelity as a measured or estimated field separate from vividness
  = must: route identity, truth, and safety-bearing recall through boundary, Security, and Honesty faculties
  = should: let visual anchors carry strong reentry cues without replacing source preservation

